## 2025-01-16
1.[bl702][bl602]Fix the crash issue occurred because one global variable was not allocated in time when ble connection was established in some corner case.

## 2024-12-24
1.[bl602][bl702]Fix the issue that blecontroller reports HCI_NB_CMP_PKTS_EVT_CODE event with wrong value of Num_Completed_Packets if there are pending acl packets that are not sent out while le link is disconnected.

