## 2024-05-21
1.[BL602][BL702]Fix the issue that it fails to allocate tx buffer in the new connection, because the previous allocated buffers are not released in the case that previous ble link is disconnected while the data is not sent out.

## 2024-04-28
1.[BL702]Fix slave's assert issue caused by that slave's remote procedure state is updated unexpectly when its llcp_phy_req is rejected by master.

